desty-al-haya","tag-obscenity-al-fahsha","tag-paradise-jannah","tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4sD","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":26443,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/21\/iman-haya-speaking-less\/","url_meta":{"origin":17151,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Modesty, speaking less are branches of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty and reticence are two branches of faith. Profanity and temerity are two branches of hypocrisy.\u201d Imam al-Tirmidhi commented, \u201cReticence is to speak little. Profanity is to speak obscenely. Temerity is to speak too often, such as those\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19342,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/17\/hereafter-jannah-nar-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":17151,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Paradise and Hellfire pray for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever asks Allah for Paradise three times, Paradise will say: O Allah, admit him into Paradise! Whoever seeks protection from Hellfire three times, Hellfire will say: O Allah, save him from the Hellfire!\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6701,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/20\/jannah-guard-jaws-legs\/","url_meta":{"origin":17151,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Lust: Paradise for controlling passions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhomever Allah protects from the evil between his jaws and the evil between his legs, he will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2409 Grade:\u00a0Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20814,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/08\/11\/tawhid-nar-first-then-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":17151,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Sinful monotheists in Hellfire, then Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSome people among those who worshiped Allah alone will be punished in Hellfire until they are coals. Then, the mercy of Allah will reach them. They will be taken out and presented at the gates of Paradise.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37215,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/25\/sahaba-bayat-al-shajarah-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":17151,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hudaybiyyah: All who pledged under the tree in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone of the companions who pledged allegiance under the tree will enter Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3860 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u0627\u064e \u064a\u064e\u062f\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062d\u064e\u062f\u064c\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17149,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/12\/haya-jamil-fashihah-ugly\/","url_meta":{"origin":17151,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Haya&#8217;: Modesty is beauty, obscenity is ugly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVulgarity is not found in anything but that it disgraces it, and modesty is not found in anything but that it beautifies it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1974 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17151","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17151"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17151\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17151"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17151"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=17151"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}